{
  "stem": "14810.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to have a indication card, so everybody had to register with a number.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in '40, 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '41, started in '41 and '42 and '43.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was a lot of people, they came out and they-- the-- the police came and they had the names.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came to the houses, hey, this party had to, by tomorrow, they have to come to the railroad station, and they have to report.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's the way they did from the beginning, But the third-- the third one, the last one, which was the largest one-- that was in 1943-- they came, and they-- with a whole company of SS came.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came with loud speakers, I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave orders-- every house, everybody, they gave you so much time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to report to that one place-- it was a special place where everybody had to report.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they told us right away anybody within, let's say it was 10 o'clock, if he doesn't show up, and if they found them, they would be executed on the spot.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So most of the people did report to the, you know, to the place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But many of them did not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was-- And then they selected people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They put them on trucks-- on-- put them to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They left 150 people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father was a good friend of the president of the Jewish Judenrat, so he allowed him to stay.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They put up a list of 150 people who can stay in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we were lucky one and they allowed us to stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I remember next morning, SS came and they start counting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Unfortunately, there was more than 150.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
